Global E-Bicycle Mid-drive Motor Market Insights
E-Bicycle Mid-drive Motor Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.5% from 2024 to 2030.

E-Bicycle Mid-drive Motor Market Overview
The global E-Bicycle Mid-drive Motor market is experiencing substantial growth, driven by increasing adoption of electric bicycles across urban and rural areas. As of 2024, the market value is projected to reach approximately USD 10.5 billion, with a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.2% from 2024 to 2030. Mid-drive motors are particularly gaining popularity due to their efficiency, superior handling, and longer lifespan compared to hub motors, making them an attractive choice for e-bike manufacturers and consumers alike. The shift towards sustainable transportation and growing demand for eco-friendly mobility solutions are expected to further bolster market expansion.

